 current and previous major releases of Chrome, Firefox, and Safari on a rolling basis. Each time a new version is released, we begin supporting that version and stop supporting the third-oldest version.&nbsp;<em style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: -webkit-auto; \">For Internet Explorer, we will support the current and two previous major releases</em>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>DESK.COM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS</h4>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: left; \"><em>Last updated Jan 11, 2013</em></p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Agent Desktop, Admin Panel, Reporting &amp; Analytics</h5>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Operating systems:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Mac 10.6.4</li>\r\n\t<li>Windows XP, Vista, 7</li>\r\n\t<li>IPad IOS 3.22</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<br />\r\n<b>Browsers:</b>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Chrome 22 &amp; 23</li>\r\n\t<li>Internet Explorer 9&nbsp;&amp; 10</li>\r\n\t<li>Firefox 16&nbsp;&amp; 17</li>\r\n\t<li>Safari 5&nbsp;&amp; 6</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div><br />\r\nCookies and Javascript must be enabled.</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Processor:&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>1 GHz or faster 32-bit or 64-bit</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Memory:&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>At least 1 GB&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Screen Resolution:</strong></div>\r\n\r\n<div>1024 x 768 for IPad</div>\r\n\r\n<div>Optimal screen resolution is 1280 x 1024 or better&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div>&nbsp;\r\n<h5>Mobile Agent Desktop</h5>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Operating systems:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>Apple iOS 3+</li>\r\n\t<li>Android 2.1+</li>\r\n\t<li>Blackberry 6+ touch devices<br />\r\n\t<em style=\"font-size: 12px;line-he