ng Captcha for Your Desk.com Help Center\n\n\n\nDesk.com supports Captcha support for all new Support Center and Widget Interactions. This feature allows you to select Always - enabling Captcha for every Support Center and Widget interaction – or Auto – enabling Captcha for these interactions automatically when conditions resembling spam submission are detected. \r\n \r\nYou can change this option within your Desk.com Admin site by visiting Settings &gt; Site Settings.\n\nNote: when created, your site is defaulted to the Auto setting. \r\n \r\nRelated Articles \r\n  \r\nOther ways to Fight Spam","body_phone_auto":true,"body_facebook":"Adding or Editing Captcha for Your Desk.com Help Center\n\n\n\nDesk.com supports Captcha support for all new Support Center and Widget Interactions. This feature allows you to select Always - enabling Captcha for every Support Center and Widget interaction – or Auto – enabling Captcha for these interactions automatically when conditions resembling spam submission are detected. \r\n \r\nYou can change this option within your Desk.com Admin site by visiting Settings &gt; Site Settings.\n\nNote: when created, your site is defaulted to the Auto setting. \r\n \r\nRelated Articles \r\n  \r\nOther ways to Fight Spam","body_facebook_auto":true,"keywords":"spam, captcha","position":11,"quickcode":null,"in_support_center":true,"internal_notes":"","publish_at":"2013-05-10T00:00:00Z","created_at":"2011-11-07T20:04:02Z","updated_at":"2013-05-13T17:57:02Z","_links":{"self":{"href":"/api/v2/articles/233449","class":"article"},"topic":{"href":"/api/v2/topics/512525","class":"topic"},"translations":{"href":"/api/v2/articles/233449/translations","class":"article_translation"}}},{"subject":"Making your Support Center your Own","body":"<body>\n<p><span>Your Support Center, in addition to providing your customer with easy access to valuable information, is also an online community for your customers to exchange information. It important that it represents 